PVRPastry is a LAN-based File Transfer application, built over a middleware 
implementation of Antony Rowstron's and Peter Druschel's PASTRY 
(http://research.microsoft.com/en-us/um/people/antr/PAST/pastry.pdf),
and it is under development.

February 2012,
Nicholas Promponas, Athens University of Economics and Business (AUEB)
Nick Vitsas, Athens University of Economics and Business (AUEB)
Panagiotis Rousis, Athens University of Economics and Business (AUEB)

